Om houm om joum om sah om bhuh om bhuvh om svah ,om Tryambakam yajamah Sugandhim pushti vardhanam Urvarukamiva bondhanan Mrityor mukshiya mamritat,om svah om bhuvh ,om bhuh om sah om joum om houm om... ..if you get this "Mrityunjay mantra plz upload it...this mantra is with 14 times "om"..i searched but i didn't get  it ...

Har..har mahadev
